description:
Stellar Frontier is a Star Trek like game. It is a free massive multiplayer game that plays like an arcade game, but with an overall strategic 

look and feel. You are in command of a single starship for a chosen civilization (Humans, Drengin, or Arceans) either offline (for fun and to 

learn how it works), or online (against or together other human players) on servers that act as other players&#039; star systems, advancing in rank 

as you gain experience. This allows you to fly different ships and try out weapons, as well as command AI-controlled ships. Get it!!! It is 

free now!!!
